item.title: LimeZ - Hectic [Trap/Dubstep; 3rd Album]
item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
Nice bass line! Chords are a bit weird. Not feeling it myself. Just keep on practicing. You’ll get it. Gotta comend you for that drop though. Awesome job there! Lobster fits well. Linda reminds me of Southborne’s Big Cat Series. Second drops use of Freak though! Wow! Never seen that done before! Awesome as always my lime!

Uniqueness: 7/10
Predictability: 8/10
Complexity: 7/10
Use of Instruments/Automation/Samples: 9/10
Feeling: 7/10

Overall: 38/50 Nice job, man. Keep up the awesome work.

~ Hexx
